{"tid":2486571,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS4 Pro Club 招人 輕鬆踢","createTime":"2021-04-13T03:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T07:15:28.000Z","uid":10225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"be8555e38097dba7747fe2df76816789bcac1036","tid":2486571,"uid":10225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:32:50.000Z","msg":"通常D1-D2，平日大槪2100 -1230，時間不定，假日可能下畫都會開下<br />\n隊波本身人唔多，有4-5個就開，online夠人就有得踢<br />\n<br />\n唔比賽，輕鬆踢，有時會開party<br />\n<br />\n想招可以踢到攻中/防中/翼嘅巴打，可以兼任多個位置更好，一個星期on到四至五日<br />\n<br />\n球隊踢法自由，少人踢就可以打長傳反擊，會傳中，多人就可以短傳連結，夾到就得<br />\n<br />\n唔要求技術好好，只需有正常足球意識，識留意隊友位置現位走位，唔獨食獨扭就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以揾呢個巴打：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/immarcoreus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fimmarcoreus&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DG9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=22c38d75\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/immarcoreus</a>"},{"pid":"5e85a25765088a00cde5030921a2225cff05da17","tid":2486571,"uid":1629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:26:36.000Z","msg":"有興趣..TG: hugo1991"},{"pid":"53b552e560d8a9ef14af81c49f72b70ea08f8538","tid":2486571,"uid":10225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e85a25765088a00cde5030921a2225cff05da17","tid":2486571,"uid":1629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:26:36.000Z","msg":"有興趣..TG: hugo1991"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58c961c0707b6a92b17d10e34eceac11622c853","tid":2486571,"uid":1629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:15:28.000Z","msg":"會唔會仲有人tg 雨狗其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji